</video>

        <p>Cesar and Mateo, two brothers struggling with financial problems, try to save their unknown neighbor's ill and aban-
doned dog Goya despite only having a few days of joy left together. Together with their friend and neighbor Camila,
they start a journey to rescue Goya from her tragic fate. The brothers have to face difficult decisions that will decide
the future of their family.</p>

